These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-1::.
Birthday: february, august, april, december
City: boston, liverpool, nizza, colone
1. Birthday:december is on the left of Birthday:february##1
2. Birthday:february is on the right of Birthday:december##1
3. City:liverpool is on the far left or far right##3
4. Birthday:april is on the right of City:nizza##1
5. City:colone is between City:liverpool and City:nizza##2
6. Birthday:december == City:boston##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |    3    |    4     |
| Birthday   | december | february     | april | august |
| City     | boston     | nizza | colone  | liverpool      |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-2::.
Flower: dahlia, bellflower, zinnia, marigold
City: edinburgh, boston, london, san-francisco
1. Flower:bellflower is on the left of City:boston##1
2. City:san-francisco is on the far left or far right##3
3. Flower:marigold is on the left of City:san-francisco##1
4. City:san-francisco is on the right of City:boston##1
5. Flower:zinnia is on the far right##1
6. City:edinburgh is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |     3      |   4   |
| Flower   | dahlia | bellflower    | marigold     | zinnia  |
| City     | edinburgh    | london | boston | san-francisco |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-3::.
