2. Birthday:april is on the far left##1
3. Transport:taxi is on the left of Birthday:may##1
4. Transport:bike is on the left or right of Birthday:december##3
5. Transport:taxi is on the right of Birthday:october##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2   |   3    |  4   |
| Birthday   | april   | october   | december  | may |
| Transport           | jet-ski | snowmobile | taxi | bike  |

