.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-4::.
House: cottage, art-deco, townhouse, colonial
Movie-Genre: zombie, disaster, scientific, epic
1. Movie-Genre:epic is on the left of House:townhouse##1
2. House:colonial is between House:cottage and Movie-Genre:scientific##2
3. House:colonial is on the left or right of House:townhouse##3
4. Movie-Genre:scientific is on the left or right of Movie-Genre:epic##3
5. House:cottage is on the right of House:art-deco##1
6. Movie-Genre:zombie is on the right of Movie-Genre:disaster##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |    3    |    4     |
| House         | art-deco | cottage | colonial | townhouse  |
| Movie-Genre   | disaster  | zombie   | epic  | scientific |

