.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-5::.
Sport: tennis, swimming, golf, rugby
Transport: quad-bike, taxi, motorbike, helicopter
1. Transport:taxi is on the far left##1
2. Sport:golf is on the right of Sport:swimming##1
3. Transport:quad-bike is on the left or right of Transport:taxi##3
4. Sport:swimming is on the right of Sport:tennis##1
5. Transport:helicopter == Sport:rugby##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |    2    |       3       |      4      |
| Sport   | tennis    | swimming   | golf | rugby    |
| Transport      | taxi | quad-bike | motorbike       | helicopter |

